response.overview: Everything is Terrible's Dante Fontana strikes back with another two-hour mix of wonderful found footage guaranteed to excite and delight. This time he has journeyed all over the galaxy to find video clips that cannot be seen anywhere else (Yes, including the internet!). God we are dying to tell you exactly what's on here but that would be against the rules. Just gather all of your friends, place the disc into your DVD player, hit play, sit back, relax, and "bliss out" as Dante take you thrilling journey directly into the great unknown.
response.title: Dante's Mystery Mix Volume 5
